    "source_url": "https://you.com/docs/research/overview",
    "comment": "Research API `research_effort`: `lite`\u2192fast, `standard`\u2192balanced (default), `deep` / `exhaustive`\u2192deep (multi-search synthesis with inline citations). Not the /v1/search SERP endpoint."
